"Using Logs you can search your logs by typing a search term, and view "
"detailed information about each event by clicking on it."
msgstr ""
"Gans Kovskrifow ty a yll hwilas dha kovskrifow gans ow jynnskrifa term "
"hwithrans, ha gweles kedhlow manylys a-dro dhe bub hwarvos gans ow klyckya "
